No. 403. Robert A. Graham, Petitioner, v. The Oregon Railroad & Navigation Company. October 19, 1908. Mr. Thomas D. Ramhaut and Mr. C. Larue Munson for petitioner. ‘ Mr. Maxwell Evarts for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States. Circuit Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.
